{{DISPLAYTITLE:List of ''Ornithogalum'' species}} The [[genus]] '''''[[Ornithogalum]]''''' contains about 180 species {{As of|2012|May|lc=on}}.<ref name=WCSP>Search for "Ornithogalum", {{Citation |title=World Checklist of Selected Plant Families |publisher=[[Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew]] |url=http://apps.kew.org/wcsp/ |accessdate=2012-05-21 }}</ref>
The ''Ornithogalum'' genus is within the [[Ornithogaleae]] tribe of the [[Scilloideae]] subfamily, in the [[Asparagaceae]] family of the [[Asparagales]] order.
