h. in V.L.Komarov (ed.)</small> *''[[Ornithogalum xanthochlorum]]'' <small>Baker in W.H.Harvey & auct. suc. (eds.)</small> *''[[Ornithogalum zebrinellum]]'' <small>U.Müll.-Doblies & D.Müll.-Doblies</small> {{colend}}
