==Most prominent summits==
{{GeoGroup|section=Most prominent summits}}
Of the most prominent summits of Oregon, [[Mount Hood]] exceeds {{convert|2000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of [[topographic prominence]].  Four peaks are [[ultra-prominent summit]]s with more than {{convert|1500|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence and 12 peaks exceed {{convert|1000|m|0|abbr=off|comma=5|sp=us}} of topographic prominence.
